subSubSection.paragraph:
Remarks. The species was until now only known from an unspecified locality in the Red Sea (
Pesta, 1911
) and from an unrecorded locality in the Dahlak Archipelago (
Neumann & Spiridonov, 1999
). It is now recorded from the Gulf of Aqaba and the Sudanese coast.
